Summary: A compiled shader file in SPIR-V format used by the RenderingDevice, distinct from Godot's Shader class.

Inherits: Resource < RefCounted < Object
Compiled shader file in SPIR-V form (used by RenderingDevice). Not to be confused with Godot's own Shader.
Note: Not to be confused with Godot's own Shader class.
