Summary: Methods for handling shader bytecode and SPIR-V versions in RDShaderFile.

- get_spirv(version: StringName = "") const → RDShaderSPIRV: Returns the SPIR-V bytecode for the specified version.
- get_version_list() const → Array[StringName]: Returns an array of available shader versions.
- set_bytecode(bytecode: RDShaderSPIRV, version: StringName = ""): Sets the shader bytecode for the specified version.
